                    </div>
                    <div class="jump-line">
                        <strong><a href="#group-sync" class="jump-link">🔄 Synchronization & Standards</a></strong>:
                        <a href="#anchor-priority-16" class="jump-link">ProjectIDs</a> |
                        <a href="#anchor-priority-efficiency" class="jump-link">ProcessEfficiency</a> |
