                    </div>
                    <div class="jump-line">
                        <strong><a href="#group-ai" class="jump-link">🤖 AI Systems</a></strong>:
                        <a href="#anchor-aichat-system" class="jump-link">AIChatSystem</a>
                    </div>
                    <div class="jump-line">
                        <strong><a href="#group-maint" class="jump-link">🛠️ Maintenance & Improvements</a></strong>:
                        <a href="#anchor-cleanup" class="jump-link">DocCleanup</a> |
                        <a href="#anchor-improvement" class="jump-link">LayoutImprovement</a> |
                        <a href="#anchor-priority-10" class="jump-link">ArchiveDocumentation</a> |
                        <a href="#anchor-priority-8" class="jump-link">APIDocUpdate</a> |
                        <a href="#anchor-priority-7" class="jump-link">AgentExample</a>
                    </div>
                    <div class="jump-line">
                        <strong><a href="#group-todo" class="jump-link">✅ Todo System</a></strong>:
